OL,3,CHow quickly are seasons warming in the
OL,4,CUK and what impact is this having?
OL,6,FNew analysis shows alarming rises in
OL,7,Fseasonal temperatures in the UK, with
OL,8,Fspring the fastest-warming climate.
OL,10,FThe average spring temperature has
OL,11,Fincreased by 1.8C since 1970,
OL,12,Faccording to Climate Central's
OL,13,Fanalysis of Met Office data, largely
OL,14,Fdue to climate change.
