OL,3,CHow quickly are seasons warming in the
OL,4,CUK and what impact is this having?
OL,6,FThe data has revealed an average
OL,7,Ftemperature rise of 1.6C in UK
OL,8,Fautumns, the average summer
OL,9,Ftemperature has increased by 1.4C and,
OL,10,Fproving that the winters of our
OL,11,Fchildhoods really were colder (and
OL,12,Flikely more snowy), the UK's average
OL,13,Fwinter temperature has increased by
OL,14,F1.3C.
OL,16,F1.8C doesn't seem like a lot - how
OL,17,Fserious is it?
