OL,3,CHow quickly are seasons warming in the
OL,4,CUK and what impact is this having?
OL,6,FAs the climate warms, the atmosphere
OL,7,Fcan hold more moisture, and this means
OL,8,Fthat here in the UK, we are now seeing
OL,9,Fmore intense and frequent rainfall,
OL,10,Fwhich in turn brings a greater risk of
OL,11,Fflooding.
OL,13,FRainfall associated with autumn and
OL,14,Fwinter storms in the UK and Ireland is
OL,15,Fbecoming more intense and more likely.
OL,16,FWe are also seeing more frequent and
OL,17,Fintense weather extremes.
OL,19,FWildlife and nature
