OL,3,CHow quickly are seasons warming in the
OL,4,CUK and what impact is this having?
OL,6,FSpring warming can have a widespread
OL,7,Fimpact on wildlife and nature, too.
OL,9,FSpring flowers in the UK are now
OL,10,Fflowering as much as a month earlier,
OL,11,Fwhich can disrupt the timing of
OL,12,Fecologically important events like
OL,13,Fpollination and migration.
OL,15,FFor instance, some species synchronise
OL,16,Ftheir migration and hibernation with
OL,17,Fthe timing of plants' flowering; early
OL,18,Fblooms can leave these species without
OL,19,Fthe flowers and plants that they rely
OL,20,Fon to survive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
