OL,3,CHow quickly are seasons warming in the
OL,4,CUK and what impact is this having?
OL,6,FThis phenomenon, known as ecological
OL,7,Fmismatch, can lead to biodiversity
OL,8,Floss if populations cannot adapt
OL,9,Fquickly enough.
OL,11,FFarming and food production
OL,13,FEarly flowering can also impact
OL,14,Ffarmers and gardeners.
OL,16,FIf fruit trees flower early, following
OL,17,Fa mild winter, entire crops can be
OL,18,Fkilled if they are hit with a late
OL,19,Ffrost.
