OL,3,CHow quickly are seasons warming in the
OL,4,CUK and what impact is this having?
OL,6,FHere, too, unprecedented amounts of
OL,7,Frain can fail entire harvests.
OL,9,FWarmer springs can also mean longer
OL,10,Fgrowing seasons.
OL,12,FAlthough some plants and animals may
OL,13,Fbenefit from this, longer growing
OL,14,Fseasons can also lead to water and
OL,15,Fheat stress in rainfed crops and
OL,16,Fdisrupt farmers' planting, irrigation,
OL,17,Fpest management, and harvest schedules
OL,18,F- all of which can have a dramatic
OL,19,Fimpact on both UK food production and
OL,20,Fcost to the consumer.
