OL,3,CHow quickly are seasons warming in the
OL,4,CUK and what impact is this having?
OL,6,FHuman impacts
OL,8,FSeasonal warming can bring on an early
OL,9,Fspring, which can also increase the
OL,10,Frisks of a longer hayfever season,
OL,11,Fwhich can have significant
OL,12,Fconsequences for human health.
OL,14,FHas this rise in seasonal temperatures
OL,15,Faffected sea temperature too?
OL,17,FYes - and this is not specific to the
OL,18,FUK.
OL,20,FAs our climate warms, the ocean is
OL,21,Fwarming too.
