OL,3,CHow quickly are seasons warming in the
OL,4,CUK and what impact is this having?
OL,6,FMelting ice sheets and glaciers are
OL,7,Fleading to sea level rise, but also,
OL,8,Fas the ocean warms, that leads to sea
OL,9,Flevel rise through thermal expansion
OL,10,F(essentially, warmer water takes up
OL,11,Fmore space than cooler water).
OL,13,FIn fact, this expansion of the oceans
OL,14,Fis responsible for between one-third
OL,15,Fand one-half of the global sea level
OL,16,Frise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
