OL,3,CHow quickly are seasons warming in the
OL,4,CUK and what impact is this having?
OL,6,FIncreased coastal flooding, erosion,
OL,7,Fand saltwater intrusion into
OL,8,Ffreshwater sources are just some of
OL,9,Fthe serious issues caused by rising
OL,10,Fsea levels, as well as the threat to
OL,11,Fhuman settlements and natural habitats
OL,12,Falong coastlines.
OL,14,FWhat is causing this seasonal rise in
OL,15,Ftemperature?
OL,17,FThe unprecedented rate of global
OL,18,Fwarming observed since the 1950s is
OL,19,Fdue primarily to emissions of heat-
OL,20,Ftrapping pollution from burning fossil
OL,21,Ffuels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
