OL,3,CHow quickly are seasons warming in the
OL,4,CUK and what impact is this having?
OL,6,FHasn't the earth experienced a level
OL,7,Fof warming before 1970?
OL,9,FYes, but the speed at which the
OL,10,Fwarming is now happening is what is so
OL,11,Falarming to experts, with data now
OL,12,Fsupporting the fact that warming
OL,13,Fglobally has been far more rapid than
OL,14,Fat any other time in at least the last
OL,15,F2000 years.
